<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361299" n="1"/>
  <note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895">Ad <abbr>Domin.</abbr> D. <rs type="person">Eglinger</rs>.</note>
<opener><lb/><salute>Vir Clarissime et Excellentissime<supplied>,</supplied> Amice charissime.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Quas ad me consolandum de funesta quam feci jactura ex obitu
  <lb/><rs type="person">Parentis</rs> mei dedisti <rs type="letter">literas</rs> mihi fuerunt gratissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>, tum quia veter<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
  <lb/>tuum erga me amicum animum abunde mihi probarunt, tum quia
  <lb/>argumentis ex Religione nostra petitis tristem meum animum<del>[...]</del>
  <lb/><del>[...]</del>si non penitus erexerunt, non leviter tamen confirmarunt. Spero Divini
  <lb/>spiritus gratiam, quam tam pio mihi apprecaris voto, suo tempore perfe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cturam <add>esse</add>, quod eloquentia tua Christiana ob fragilitatem meam
  <lb/>fortassis nondum efficere potuit. Vix enim est, ut ex vulnere hoc
  <lb/>non una ratione gravissimo convalescam, nisi Deus <abbr>O. M.</abbr> opem
  <lb/>ferat, cujus proinde voluntati ut me unice co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>ittam, <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quum est.
  <lb/>Monitum illud <rs type="person">Epictetium</rs> <foreign xml:lang="grc">ἀνέχου καὶ ἀπέχου</foreign><note type="editorial">Stoische Lebensregel: "Ertrage und enthalte dich".</note>, quod in memoriam
  <lb/>mihi revocas ad <foreign xml:lang="grc">πράξιν</foreign> transferre pro viribus conabor, Deum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
  <lb/>precabor, ut ulteriores calamitates quas ob monitum illud ne<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>glectum me meruisse confiteor <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me auferat. Me <del>[...]</del>etiam
  <lb/>Te <del>[...]</del><add>et</add> <rs type="person">famili<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice></rs> honoratissim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> diutissime incolumem conser<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vet omnique vera prosperitate beet,<!-- ToDo: kontrollieren beet. --> et inprimis <add>firma valetudine donet</add> Amplissimos
  <lb/><abbr>Dnos</abbr> <rs type="person">Socerum</rs> et <rs type="person">Prosocerum</rs> Tuum, <del>[...]</del>quibus si <add>data occasione</add> debit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
  <lb/>obsequii et honoris cultum meo nomine offeres, gratum mihi facies.
  <lb/>Salutem dic quoque, <add>si</add> placet, <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Affini</rs> Tuo, cujus ut et Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>
  <lb/>me porro co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endo. Vix quisquam est ex <rs type="person">Professoribus</rs> nostris,
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo novi quid tibi non displiciturum sperare liceat, nisi forte
  <lb/>ab Anatomico nostro <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Morgagni</rs>, Viro perhumano et mihi ami<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>co. Si quid ab illo vel alio Auctore scitu dignum prodeat tecum co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>u<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nicab<del>[...]</del><add>i</add>t Tuus, quem ad omnia officia paratum habes,</p>
<closer><lb/><signed><rs type="person">NB.</rs></signed>
<dateline><date when="1717-02-24">24. <abbr>Febr.</abbr> 1717</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
